name: Rathtar
comments: Among the most dangerous creatures in the galaxy

name: Huna-netre
comments: Claws that can slice throught Carbonite

name: Lylek
comments: A native of the Ryloth equatorial rain forests, they usually grwo to immense size, big enough to eat a full-grown man.

name: Vexis
comments: Armored Snake that burrows its way beneath the sands of Pasaana. The oil it excretes from its skin hardens the sand it travels through, creating a growing network of tunnels.

name: Milodon
comments: Insect with giant glowing eyes and pincers on its face.

name: Wooriid
comments: Large amphibious Beast. A slow-moving carnivore gifted with massive jaws full of razor-sharp teeth.  There are neurotoxins secreted by the Wooriid's slimy skin that rendered paralyzed.

name: Sanval
comments: Gigantic winged reptile that was older than time and rumored to never forget a face

name: Hragscythe
comments: Six eyes, eighteen claws, three heads, and more teeth than a pack of nexus
